reviewText: T​his course uses the Coursera Rhyme platform, which doesn't seem to be well designed. The interface isn't intuitive. Unfortunately, the course instructor doesn't show anyone how to access the files, she gives about 2 verbal sentences and that was it. As I was trying to figure it out on my own I moved past a download page, and now I'm unable to get back. For some reason I can't unenroll either.B​ased on the comments in the forums, many people have had the same issue with being unable to download the files.
